---
import { Image } from "@astrojs/image/components";
import Layout from "../layout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy";
const description = "About the privacy policy of the app.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="max-w-[600px] mx-auto px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl text-primary text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="text-md text-primary mt-12">
      Please note that this Privacy Policy provides details to users who have
      previously engaged with our application. It outlines the nature of the
      information we gather, the reasons behind its collection, and the
      procedures we adopt for data disposal upon service termination.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl text-primary mt-12">1. Collection and Usage</h2>

    <h3 class="text-xl text-primary mt-8 pl-4 border-l-4 border-primary">Data Provided by Users</h3>

    <p class="text-md text-primary mt-4">
      In this application, we are collecting the following data from our users:
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc text-md text-primary mt-4 ml-4">
      <li>Unique Nickname</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl text-primary mt-8 pl-4 border-l-4 border-primary">DataÂ Provided During Game Play</h3>

    <p class="text-md text-primary mt-4">
      The information provided when playing games in this application is as
      follows:
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc text-md text-primary mt-4 ml-4">
      <li>Scores for each song and level by the player</li>
      <li>Last login date</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl text-primary mt-8 pl-4 border-l-4 border-primary">Purpose of Using the Data</h3>

    <p class="text-md text-primary mt-4">
      The collected data is used for user identification while ensuring
      anonymity, providing a scoring function, and cleaning up information of
      long-term inactive users.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl text-primary mt-12">2. Data Erasure</h2>

    <p class="text-md text-primary mt-4">
      The data collected as described above was completely deleted as of April
      17, 2024.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl text-primary mt-12">3. Contact Information</h2>

    <p class="text-md text-primary mt-4">
      If you have any questions or concerns about privacy, please contact the
      following.
      <br />
      <br />
      Email: support@ikep.dev
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
